comments: Ellis (SAC) has a hand placed on Williams' (OKC) side and marginal contact occurs as he releases the driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAC) briefly places both hands on Dort (OKC) when Dort pursues the rebound, but he is not dislodged from his position.
Sabonis (SAC) grabs and holds Holmgren (OKC), affecting his ability to pursue the rebound.
Holmgren (OKC) brushes Ellis' (SAC) arm as he pursues the rebound and the contact is marginal.
Holmgren (OKC) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds and SAC should be given possession.
Holmgren (OKC) is firming up in Mitchell's (SAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) moves his pivot foot before entering his shooting motion.
Mitchell (SAC) has his right arm extended forwards when Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC) leans into him to initiate the marginal arm contact.
Sabonis (SAC) firms up over to his left leg in Dort's (OKC) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Although Mitchell (SAC) makes contact with the ball, he reaches across Gilgeous-Alexander's (OKC) arm and initiates illegal contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holmgren (OKC) jumps vertically and absorbs the contact with Ellis (SAC) as he makes the pass.
Ellis (SAC) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (OKC).
